# Knowledge Updater Cron Configuration
# Schedule weekly automated knowledge base updates

# Weekly update every Sunday at 2 AM (system time)
0 2 * * 0 cd /path/to/microservices-architecture-audit && python tools/knowledge_updater.py >> logs/knowledge_update.log 2>&1

# Alternative: Run every Monday at 3 AM
# 0 3 * * 1 cd /path/to/microservices-architecture-audit && python tools/knowledge_updater.py >> logs/knowledge_update.log 2>&1

# Alternative: Run every 7 days from last run (not cron-specific)
# Use systemd timer or task scheduler instead

# Linux/Systemd Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to /etc/cron.d/knowledge-updater
# 2. Ensure the path is correct for your installation
# 3. Ensure python3 and dependencies are installed
# 4. Ensure logs directory exists and is writable

